Third-party data (runtime only — NOT covered by this Apache-2.0 license)
================================================================================

Aniseekr is a client that queries third-party catalogues at runtime. The
catalogue content (titles, posters, synopses, tags, scene coordinates, etc.)
belongs to its respective providers and is governed by their own terms.

  - Anitabi (聖地巡礼 scene coordinates and screenshots)
      Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 by the Anitabi community.
      https://anitabi.cn  ·  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/
      The Aniseekr app surfaces Anitabi attribution on every screen that
      renders Anitabi-sourced data (detail, sheet, scene tiles, compare flow).

  - Bangumi (bgm.tv)            https://bangumi.github.io/api/
  - AniList                     https://docs.anilist.co/
  - MyAnimeList (via Jikan)     https://jikan.moe/
  - Kitsu                       https://kitsu.docs.apiary.io/
  - Annict                      https://developers.annict.com/
  - Simkl                       https://simkl.docs.apiary.io/
  - Shikimori                   https://shikimori.one/api/doc
  - Anime Tourism 88            https://animetourism88.com/

These are queried at runtime; their data is not redistributed inside this
repository. If you fork Aniseekr and ship it under a different brand, you are
responsible for honouring each upstream provider's terms of service.
